Data Protection
Declaration
welcome to our app and website!
We value your privacy and the protection of your data. We are committed to not disclosing your personal information to third parties under any circumstances.
This data protection declaration (hereinafter "Declaration") explains how we collect, process and use personal data.
1. Data Controller
The data controller for the purposes of the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) is:
HERMMAN Commerce GmbH
Mercatorstraße 1b, 47051 Duisburg
0049(0)203-47955990
service@dajiangyou.eu
2. Data Collection
We collect personal data that you voluntarily provide to us when using our app or website. This includes:
Name, address and contact details
Information about your orders and transactions
Information about your devices and browsers
Log data about your use of the app or website
3. Data Use
We only use your personal data for the following purposes:
To provide our app and website
To fulfill your orders and transactions
To improve our app and website
To ensure the security of our app and website
To comply with legal obligations
Data Disclosure
We only disclose your personal data in the following cases:
If you have given your express consent to the disclosure
If it is necessary to fulfill your orders and transactions
If we are legally obligated to disclose the data
If the disclosure is necessary to protect our legitimate interests or those of third parties
4. Data Storage
We store your personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected, or as required by law.
5. Data Security
We take appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, misuse, loss or destruction.
6. Your Rights
You have the right to access, rectify, delete or restrict the processing of your personal data. You also have the right to object to the processing of your personal data. To exercise your rights, please contact us using the contact information provided in this declaration.
7. Contact
If you have any questions or concerns regarding the processing of your personal data, please contact us at the following address:
HERMMAN Commerce GmbH
Mercatorstraße 1b, 47051 Duisburg
0049(0)203-47955990
service@dajiangyou.eu
We hope this data protection declaration provides you with a clear understanding of how we collect, process, and use your personal data.
隐私声明
欢迎使用我们的应用程序和网站！我们重视您的隐私和数据保护。我们承诺在任何情况下都不会向第三方披露您的个人信息。
此隐私声明（以下简称“声明”）解释了我们如何收集、处理和使用个人数据。
数据控制者
